<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>346</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw van lam hetna lul chuh,
 Leia sanga sang zaw;
 Isu-a Pa hehpihna,
 Tawp neilo a tam chuh.

[V2]
 Heta ginchak, kipak a pawm,
 Thumak tak, mak tak mai chuh;
 Hehpih a um, Pathien a um,
 Thisan a ngaihdam, thiensak.

[V3]
 2. Pathien Thun zie hetna hi,
 I kawmah A phuong tai;
 Pathien Thu chun a phuonga,
 Pathien tiemteh a chun.

[V4]
 3. Ginna ziekin I mu tau,
 Pathien mi lungsietna;
 Kalvari-ah I gingchau,
 Gitloh a ngaihdam in.

[V5]
 4. Eimau ah Thagau a cheng,
 Chunglam thil ei hetsak;
 Hehpihna thu chuh ei hilh,
 Krista Pa hehpihna.</lyrics>
<title>DWELLING IN LOVE</title>
</song>